main event: A UFO report from October 1962, associated with Project Blue Book, features photographs of mountainous and hilly terrain in North Carolina.
interesting points: The report references three photographs, Two photos show hilly terrain without any visible human presence, One photo displays a scenic landscape captured in black and white, The source of the report is the Foreign Technology Division of AFSC, The document is classified as UNCLASSIFIED.
witness description: no human faces or individuals visible in the images
